[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "But lay up for yourselves treasures in heaven, where neither moth nor rust doth corrupt, and where thieves do not break through nor steal.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Let us try to understand him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "It has to be sought for because of its depth at once and its simplicity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "But it is so complete, so imaginatively comprehensive, so immediately operative on the conscience through its poetic suggestiveness, that when it is once understood, there is nothing more to be said, but everything to be done.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "\"Why not lay up for ourselves treasures upon earth?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "\"Because there the moth and rust and the thief come.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "\"Yes; by the moth and the rust and the thief.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "\"Of course the heart will be where the treasure is; but what has that to do with the argument?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "This: that what is with the treasure must fare as the treasure; that the heart which haunts the treasure house where the moth and rust corrupt, will be exposed to the same ravages as the treasure, will itself be rusted and moth eaten.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Many a man, many a woman, fair and flourishing to see, is going about with a rusty moth eaten heart within that form of strength or beauty.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "\"But this is only a figure.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "True.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "But is the reality intended, less or more than the figure?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10798_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10798/4010_10798_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Therein lies the hurt.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Was it the cry of relief at the touch of death?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Was it the cry of victory?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000005_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000005_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "It may have been all in one.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000005_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000005_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "And the mighty story ends with a cry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Every highest human act is just a giving back to God of that which he first gave to us.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000006_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000006_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "I am thine, and therefore I am mine.'\" The vast operations of the spiritual as of the physical world, are simply a turning again to the source.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000009_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000009_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Am I going to do a good deed?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000009_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000009_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Am I going to die?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000009_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000009_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Thou knowest, if only from the cry of thy Son, how terrible that is; and if it comes not to me in so terrible a shape as that in which it came to him, think how poor to bear I am beside him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000009_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000009_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "I do not know what the struggle means; for, of the thousands who pass through it every day, not one enlightens his neighbour left behind; but shall I not long with agony for one breath of thy air, and not receive it?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000009_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000009_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Thou wilt know every shade of my suffering; thou wilt care for me with thy perfect fatherhood; for that makes my sonship, and inwraps and infolds it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000009_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000009_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "I care not for the pain, so long as my spirit is strong, and into thy hands I commend that spirit.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Think, brothers, think, sisters, we walk in the air of an eternal fatherhood.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Whither else dare we send them?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "How the earthly father would love a child who would creep into his room with angry, troubled face, and sit down at his feet, saying when asked what he wanted: \"I feel so naughty, papa, and I want to get good\"!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Would he say to his child: \"How dare you!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000011_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000011_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Go away, and be good, and then come to me?\" And shall we dare to think God would send us away if we came thus, and would not be pleased that we came, even if we were angry as jonah?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000011_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000011_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Bread, at least, will be given, and not a stone; water, at least, will be sure, and not vinegar mingled with gall.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "We may commend any brother, any sister, to the common fatherhood.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10801_000012_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10801/4010_10801_000012_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "For he cannot be our father save as he is their father; and if we do not see him and feel him as their father, we cannot know him as ours.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "The question is called forth by what the Lord had just said concerning his kingdom, closing with the statement that it was not of this world.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "He might have had them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000003_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000003_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "He did not care for government.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000003_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000003_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Government, I repeat, was to him flat, stale, unprofitable.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000004_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000004_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "His subjects must be of his own kind, in their very nature and essence kings.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000004_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000004_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "To understand his answer to Pilate, see wherein consists his kingship; what it is that makes him a king; what manifestation of his essential being gives him a claim to be king.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000004_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000004_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "The Lord's is a kingdom in which no man seeks to be above another: ambition is of the dirt of this world's kingdoms.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000004_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000004_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Neither Pilate nor they ask the one true question, 'How am I to be a true man?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000004_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000004_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "They will kill him, but it matters not: the truth is as he says!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Jesus is a king because his business is to bear witness to the truth. What truth?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000005_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000005_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "My judgment is the faultless rule of things.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000005_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000005_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "My right is-what I desire. The more I am all in all to myself, the greater I am.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000005_000016",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000005_000016.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "My will is all for his will, for his will is right.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000005_000017",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000005_000017.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "He is righteousness itself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000005_000022",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000005_000022.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "He is the truth, and I am the truth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000005_000025",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000005_000025.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "I fear nothing you can do to me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000005_000028",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000005_000028.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "You do not like to hear it because you are not like him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000005_000029",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000005_000029.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "I am low in your eyes which measure things by their show; therefore you say I blaspheme.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000005_000032",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000005_000032.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "I came into the world to show him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "If I mistake, he will forgive me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Of the men who before Christ bare witness to the truth, some were sawn asunder, some subdued kingdoms; it mattered nothing which: they witnessed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "The truth is God; the witness to the truth is Jesus.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "The thought of God is the truth of everything.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000008_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000008_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "The man who responds to this with his whole being, is of the truth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "When his witness is treated as a lie, then most he witnesses, for he gives it still.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Is every Christian expected to bear witness?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000010_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000010_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "Are we careful to be true?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4010_10822_000010_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4010/10822/4010_10822_000010_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4010",
        "content": "When contempt is cast on the truth, do we smile?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
